  <ns0:data key="d2">Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the contract solicitation document, spanning pages 13 to 21, detailing option line items and Section F provisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation number for the contract, referenced in file names and attachments.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation N6945025R0003 is a procurement document for Mayport BOS services, incorporating various FAR and DFARS clauses and provisions for offerors.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the overall contract solicitation document referenced on binder covers.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation N6945025R0003 is the procurement solicitation that includes attachments for facility inventories and Section K for representations and certifications.</ns0:data>
