  <ns0:data key="d1">submission_instruction</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Pre-Award Inquiry Cutoff is established at 2:00 PM EDT on Thursday, 02 October 2025 for submitting all Government Preaward Inquiries.</ns0:data>
