  <ns0:data key="d0">Attachment J-0200000-17</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d1">document</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Attachment J-0200000-17 is an Excel spreadsheet containing worksheets for Exhibit Line Item Numbers corresponding to each Contract Line Item, used for pricing recurring and non-recurring work.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment J-0200000-17 provides worksheet tabs for exhibit line item numbers and sub-ELINs used in option line items, with instructions to use the most current version and check amendments.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment J-0200000-17 is the Exhibit Line Item Numbers used for pricing spreadsheet data.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e</ns0:data>
