  <ns0:data key="d1">section</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Section C specifies the places of work performance, referenced in Section F for locations at Naval Station Mayport Jacksonville and Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island.&lt;SEP&gt;Section C covers Description/Specifications/Statement of Work for the performance-based contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Section C in Annex 1700000 outlines transportation limits of liability and maintenance requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Section C identifies the key personnel whose substitutions require Contracting Officer approval.&lt;SEP&gt;Section C covers Description/Specifications/Work Statement.</ns0:data>
