  <ns0:data key="d1">section</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Section I incorporates various FAR clauses by reference, covering definitions, gratuities, ethics, reporting, and prohibitions.&lt;SEP&gt;Section I contains Contract Clauses.</ns0:data>
