  <ns0:data key="d1">section</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">List of Attachments, including documents, exhibits, and other attachments posted on the SAM website with the solicitation, covering acquisition and technical documents.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J contains the Exhibit Line Item Number (ELIN) Pricing Attachment with multiple worksheets for completion and electronic submission.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J describes the systems approach in the solicitation, requiring demonstration of understanding in the offeror's methodology.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J provides ELINs that support the unit price tasks in Section B for ordering via FedMall.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J contains ELINs that support the supplies and services in Section B for the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J is the List of Attachments.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J includes attachments such as the ELIN pricing spreadsheet.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e</ns0:data>
