  <ns0:data key="d1">clause</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">FAR 52.215-1 Instructions to Offerors-Competitive Acquisition is a clause incorporated by reference effective November 2021, with Alternate I from October 1997.&lt;SEP&gt;FAR 52.215-1 addresses late submissions, modifications, and withdrawals for negotiated solicitations.&lt;SEP&gt;FAR 52.215-1 provides instructions to offerors for competitive acquisition, modified by L.11 for all or none offers.</ns0:data>
