  <ns0:data key="d1">deliverable</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Indefinite Quantity Pre-Priced Line Item Services are offered by the contractor through Fedmall for government purchase card orders under Section B, supported by Section J ELINs.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</ns0:data>
