<ns0:edge source="Government" target="Liquidated Damages">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Liquidated damages are paid to the Government to cover administrative costs and expenses from the Contractor's nonperformance.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government assesses liquidated damages against the Contractor for non-performed work to cover administrative costs.</ns0:data>
