  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">WG-10 Boiler Tender is identified as a service employee class with equivalent monetary wage-fringe benefits under 52.222-42 Statement of Equivalent Rates for Federal Hires.</ns0:data>
