  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Section K includes the full text of clause 52.204-8 to guide offerors on completing annual representations and certifications.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">full text,incorporation</ns0:data>
