  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">DFARS 215.304(c)(i) requires small businesses identified in evaluations to be listed in the SBSP.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">evaluation integration,listing requirement</ns0:data>
