  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The FAR incorporates clause 52.215-20 by reference and full text for certified cost or pricing data submissions.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">incorporation,pricing data requirements</ns0:data>
