  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The DFARS provides clause 252.215-7008 for handling only one offer, requiring additional cost or pricing data.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">data submission,sole offer handling</ns0:data>
